menu_buildjob_depot
[TITLE]The Manual:  Trade Depot Menu[/TITLE]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_BUILDJOB] from the main view and move to a trade depot.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
If merchants are coming, you can bring goods to the trade depot.
[B]
If merchants have arrived and unloaded their goods, you can trade with them.
[B]
When trading, you select goods on both sides of the partition.  Then you can trade.
The merchant will give you feedback.
[B]
You can seize goods from a merchant.  This will cause tensions between your civilizations.
[B]
You can offer goods to a merchant.  This will smooth over tensions somewhat and generally improve relations.  You shouldn't offer
goods to dwarves, as this currently does nothing (with one clear exception late game).
